Simple examples of using CABasicAnimation and gestures.

While the wife's away... I'll write iOS? O_o

* Swipe up/down/left/right - moves the square in the swipe direction
* Single Tap - rotate 360
* Double Tap - fades out
* Pinch/Zoom - scales the square - not too hot right now
* Rotate - rotates the sqaure - again not too hot
* Two finger tap - reset
* Tap and hold the square to drag it around